<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-style> h2, img, p { margin: 0; } td { padding-top: 0 !important; } p { margin-bottom: 10px; } </mj-style>
    <mj-font name="Roboto" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" />
    <mj-font name="Roboto+Serif" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Serif:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..144,100..900;1,8..144,100..900&display=swap" />
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body background-color="#f0f1f3">
    
    <mj-spacer height="15px"></mj-spacer>
    <!-- Logo Header -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff"  >
    <mj-spacer height="10px" />
      <mj-column  padding="10px 12px 10px 12px" width="100%" > 
        <mj-spacer height="16px" />
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" css-class="light_img" width="150px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/logo.png" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" alt="" />
            

        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 2px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              margin-top:2px;
            ">Did you know the President of the United States receives a top-secret briefing on national security every morning?</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
            "><strong>On 4th Jan 2025 weekend edition:</strong></p>
            <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              padding-left:10px;
            ">→ Schengen’s new members</p>
            <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              padding-left:10px;
            ">→ HIV summer camp closes</p>
            <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              padding-left:10px;
            ">→ New Orleans makeshift memorial</p>
            
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="0px 0px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-spacer height="10px"></mj-spacer>

    <!-- THE BIG ONE-->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_fsection" background-color="#ffffff" css-class="mj_fsection">
      <mj-spacer height="0px"></mj-spacer>
      <mj-column background-color="#ffffff" width="100%">
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px 0px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="white">
          <h2 style="
          color:#4D3060;
            text-align: left;
            letter-spacing:6px;
            border-bottom:2px solid #4D3060;
            text-transform:uppercase;
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              font-weight: 300;
              padding: 18px 8px 10px 8px;
              
            ">THE BIG ONE</h2>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- THE BIG ONE contents-->

    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;
            ">2025 violent opener</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/ps-jan-4-1.jpg" alt="2025 violent opener" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">The US didn’t have a very peaceful entry into 2025, as multiple acts of violence happened on January 1st. In <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-04-01-2025-h1-1-new-orleans" target="_blank">New Orleans</a>, a man drove a white Ford pickup truck flying the flag of ISIS into a group of those celebrating the New Year, killing 14 people. Just a few hours later, a Tesla cyber truck <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-04-01-2025-h1-2-exploded" target="_blank">exploded</a> in front of the Trump Hotel. The FBI eventually concluded they were unrelated, which has put many on edge. There was a <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-04-01-2025-h1-3-shooting" target="_blank">shooting</a> at a New York nightclub on New Year's Day where there were no deaths, but 10 were injured.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px)">While the US seems notably unlucky, Europe also had its share of violence. <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-04-01-2025-h1-4-montenegro" target="_blank">Montenegro</a> had a mass shooting that resulted in the death of 12 people. Germany saw <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-04-01-2025-h5-5-five-deaths" target="_blank">five deaths</a> and 400 arrests related to catastrophic fireworks and riots, which prompted discussions on private firework ownership bans. </p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
     <mj-spacer height="15px"></mj-spacer>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>